Class SavedSimulation

java.lang.Object
  simzombie.engine.SavedSimulation
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SavedSimulation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Class that structures a Simulation in a way that it can be saved Simulation IO uses this class, which saves an ordered list of SavedStep objects which relate to the individual steps of a simulation. From this class, an entire simulation can be recreated, and is used for both storing simulations and allowing for replayability of simulations as they are running
